('4390', '13', 'Source:Recipe Copyright Sasha Martin, Global Table Adventure. For personal or educational use only.'),
('4391', '1', 'Place eggs in a single layer in a saucepan. cover with water. Bring to a simmer over medium-high heat. Reduce heat to low and cook at the barest simmer for 10 minutes.'),
('4391', '2', 'Remove from heat, pour out hot water and run a constant stream of cold water over the eggs until completely cooled.Nutrition'),
